{"tid":1058953,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗恥笑區","createTime":"2019-03-13T00:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T00:07:40.000Z","uid":182047,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1ceb4c5997fe1e7d8001e2fca5b053944adbba4f","tid":1058953,"uid":182047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T00:07:40.000Z","msg":"C朗冇入波 -&gt; 笑佢冇入波 <br />\n<br />\nC朗對弱隊入波 -&gt; 笑佢對弱隊刷數據 <br />\n<br />\nC朗對強隊入波 -&gt; 睇佢有冇靠十二碼、tap in、頭槌，有就笑佢淨係識靠十二碼、搶點、頭槌 <br />\n<br />\nC朗入波但冇靠十二碼、tap in、頭槌 -&gt; 睇佢有冇助攻，冇就笑佢獨食 <br />\n<br />\nC朗有入波又有助攻 -&gt; 睇隊友入波後，佢有冇慶祝，冇就笑佢黑面，淨係掛住自己入波<br />\n<br />\nC朗有助攻但冇入波 -&gt; 笑佢冇入波<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6205786&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6205786%26page%3D1&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0La%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=8c0dddac\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6205786&amp;page=1</a>"}]}